definition: Liaoyang prefecture-level city in Liaoning province 遼寧省|辽宁省 in northeast China
short name for Liaoning 遼寧|辽宁[Liao2 ning2] province/Liao or Khitan dynasty (907-1125)

sentences.english: The ecological sensitivity assessment of soil erosion in Liaoyang city was conducted.
sentences.chinese: 選擇土壤侵蝕進行遼陽市的生態敏感性評價。
